Let me analyze the images and provide a detailed solution:

Main Target Image Analysis:
- Total Blocks: 11 blocks
- Colors: Red, Yellow, Green, Blue, Orange
- Layers: 2 main layers
- Structure: Complex arrangement with arches, columns, and stacked blocks

Block Selection from Dictionary:

1. Block 1 (Red arch) - 2 times
2. Block 2 (Red angled block)
3. Block 3 (Blue cube)
4. Block 4 (Orange cube)
5. Block 5 (Orange cube)
6. Block 6 (Green rectangular block)
7. Block 7 (Green rectangular block)
8. Block 8 (Yellow rectangular block) - 2 times
9. Block 9 (Yellow rectangular block)
10. Block 10 (Orange cylinder)
11. Block 11 (Yellow half-cylinder)
12. Block 12 (Yellow half-cylinder)
13. Block 13 (Orange cube)
14. Block 14 (Orange cube)
15. Block 15 (Orange angled block)
16. Block 16 (Orange angled block/triangle)

Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block 1 (Red arch)
    Step2: Move block 8 (Yellow rectangular block) on top of block 1
    Step3: Move block 10 (Orange cylinder) on the yellow block
    Step4: Move block 1 (Another Red arch) beside first arch
    Step5: Move block 11 (Yellow half-cylinder) on first arch
    Step6: Move block 3 (Blue cube) next to first structure
    Step7: Move block 6 (Green rectangular block) next to blue cube
    Step8: Move block 8 (Another Yellow rectangular block) to complete lower layer
    Step9: Add block 4, 5, 13, 14 (Orange cubes) to stabilize lower layer
    Step10: Add block 12 (Yellow half-cylinder) on top
    Step11: Add block 15 and 16 (Orange angled blocks) to complete top layer
}
